data.description: Fantastic home in The Coves backing to the wooded area/creek. This well maintained home offers open, one-level living with granite countertops in the kitchen, hardwood floors, stainless appliances, a private deck, and a finished walk-out basement with media room. Washer and dryer hook-ups in the primary and a full utility room in the basement. Let the HOA take care of mowing the lawn and removing snow.  HOA also pays for the water for the sprinkler system.  Near Rock Chalk Park, I-70/K-10 for easy access.  Check it out today!!! 2023-11-17
